    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 71.78%. MAD River Investors's largest holding is Texas Pacific Land Trust with shares held of 41,675.   WhaleWisdom has at least 43 13Fs and  3 13D/G filings in our database for MAD River Investors. 
                                           














