Mad River Investors Buys Liberty Ventures Group, Lions Gate Entertainment, Liberty Expedia Holdings, Sells Starz, Platform Specialty Products, Sears CanadaFebruary 13, 2017 |  About: 
LVNTA  +0%
LGF.B  +0%
LEXEA  +0%
EMGC  +0%
STRZA  +0% 



Boston, MA, based Investment company Mad River Investors buys Liberty Ventures Group, Lions Gate Entertainment, Liberty Expedia Holdings, Emergent Capital, sells Starz, Platform Specialty Products, Sears Canada during the 3-months ended 2016-12-31, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Mad River Investors. As of 2016-12-31, Mad River Investors owns 33 stocks with a total value of $77 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: LVNTA, LGF.B, LEXEA, EMGC, Added Positions: DISH, IEP, SATS, Reduced Positions: PAH, SHLD, SRSC, NVGS, BRK.B, PGLC, LSXMK, CLR, LBRDK, GRBK, Sold Out: STRZA, Warning! GuruFocus has detected 5 Warning Signs with LVNTA. Click here to check it out. 
LVNTA 30-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of LVNTAPeter Lynch Chart of LVNTAFor the details of MAD RIVER INVESTORS's stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=MAD+RIVER+INVESTORSThese are the top 5 holdings of MAD RIVER INVESTORSTexas Pacific Land Trust (TPL) - 41,565 shares, 15.92% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 0.66%The Howard Hughes Corp (HHC) - 87,268 shares, 12.85% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 0.71%Icahn Enterprises LP (IEP) - 136,159 shares, 10.53% of the total portfolio.  Shares added by 1.71%Berkshire Hathaway Inc (BRK.B) - 39,004 shares, 8.21% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 1.39%Liberty SiriusXM Group (LSXMK) - 142,941 shares, 6.26% of the total portfolio.  Shares reduced by 1.17%New Purchase: Liberty Ventures Group (LVNTA)Mad River Investors initiated holdings in  Liberty Ventures Group.  The purchase prices were between $36.87 and $41.22, with an estimated average price of $39.29.   The stock is now traded at around $43.90. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 3.83%. The holdings were 80,408 shares as of 2016-12-31. New Purchase: Lions Gate Entertainment Corp (LGF.B)Mad River Investors initiated holdings in  Lions Gate Entertainment Corp.  The purchase prices were between $18.58 and $26.37, with an estimated average price of $22.53.   The stock is now traded at around $26.50. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 1.45%. The holdings were 45,680 shares as of 2016-12-31. New Purchase: Liberty Expedia Holdings Inc (LEXEA)Mad River Investors initiated holdings in  Liberty Expedia Holdings Inc.  The purchase prices were between $39.32 and $45, with an estimated average price of $42.49.   The stock is now traded at around $43.80. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.57%. The holdings were 11,229 shares as of 2016-12-31. New Purchase: Emergent Capital Inc (EMGC)Mad River Investors initiated holdings in  Emergent Capital Inc.  The purchase prices were between $1.12 and $2.93, with an estimated average price of $2.04.   The stock is now traded at around $0.28. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.22%. The holdings were 141,374 shares as of 2016-12-31. Sold Out: Starz (STRZA)Mad River Investors sold out the holdings in  Starz.  The sale prices were between $30.45 and $35.52, with an estimated average price of $32.47. Here is the complete portfolio of MAD RIVER INVESTORS. Also check out:
